      "source": "in the style of Schaum's Outline of Calculus"
    },
    {
      "id": "calculus-ii-integration-techniques-027",
      "stem": "Which technique evaluates $\\displaystyle\\int \\frac{x}{x^2 + 1}\\,dx$ most directly?",
